            <p>Reserve your equipment in just a few clicks.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <i class="bi bi-calendar-check fs-1 mb-3"></i>
            <h4>Real-Time Availability</h4>
            <p>Always know what’s available when you need it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <i class="bi bi-shield-lock fs-1 mb-3"></i>
            <h4>Secure & Reliable</h4>
            <p>Safe transactions with verified users and staff.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

